// client/src/pages/Home/Home.js
import React from 'react';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import { motion } from 'framer-motion';
import { Box, Typography, Grid, Card, CardContent, Avatar, Button, LinearProgress, IconButton } from '@mui/material';
import KeyboardArrowDownIcon from '@mui/icons-material/KeyboardArrowDown';
import './Home.css';

const profiles = [
  {
    key: 'maria',
    name: 'Maria Elheeb',
    role: 'Fullstack Developer | React | Node.js',
    img: 'icon2.png',
  },
  {
    key: 'yazan',
    name: 'Yazan Dawud',
    role: 'Software Engineer | JavaScript | Express',
    img: 'icon1.png',
  },
];

const techStack = [
  { name: 'React', icon: '/assets/react-icon.svg' },
  { name: 'Node.js', icon: '/assets/nodejs-icon.svg' },
  { name: 'Material UI', icon: '/assets/mui-icon.svg' },
  { name: 'Bootstrap', icon: '/assets/bootstrap-icon.svg' },
];

const Home = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  return (
    <Box className="home-hero">
      <motion.div
        className="hero-content"
        initial={{ opacity: 0, y: -50 }}
        animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
        transition={{ duration: 0.8 }}
      >
        <Typography variant="h2" component="h1" gutterBottom>
          Welcome to Our Portfolio
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1" gutterBottom>
          Choose a profile to explore:
        </Typography>
      </motion.div>

      <IconButton
        className="scroll-down"
        onClick={() =>
          window.scrollTo({ top: window.innerHeight, behavior: 'smooth' })
        }
      >
        <KeyboardArrowDownIcon fontSize="large" />
      </IconButton>

      <Grid container justifyContent="center" spacing={4} className="profile-grid">
        {profiles.map((p) => (
          <Grid item key={p.key} xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <motion.div whileHover={{ scale: 1.05 }} whileTap={{ scale: 0.95 }}>
              <Card className="profile-card" onClick={() => navigate(`/projects?user=${p.key}`)} elevation={6}>
                <CardContent>
                  <Avatar src={p.img} alt={p.name} className="profile-avatar" />
                  <Typography variant="h5" component="h3" mt={2}>
                    {p.name}
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" mt={1}>
                    {p.role}
                  </Typography>
                  <Button variant="outlined" className="explore-button" sx={{ mt: 3 }}>
                    Explore
                  </Button>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </motion.div>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>

      <Box className="about-me-section">
        <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
          About Me
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
          I'm a passionate full-stack developer specializing in React and Node.js.
          I love crafting performant, responsive, and visually engaging web applications.
        </Typography>
        <Button variant="contained" onClick={() => navigate('/about')}>
          Learn More
        </Button>
      </Box>

      <Box className="tech-stack-section">
        <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
          Tech Stack
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center">
          {techStack.map((tech) => (
            <Grid item key={tech.name} xs={6} sm={3}>
              <motion.div whileHover={{ scale: 1.1 }}>
                <Card className="tech-card" elevation={3}>
                  <CardContent className="tech-card-content">
                    <Avatar src={tech.icon} alt={tech.name} className="tech-icon" />
                    <Typography variant="subtitle2" mt={1}>
                      {tech.name}
                    </Typography>
                    <LinearProgress variant="determinate" value={80} className="tech-progress" />
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </motion.div>
            </Grid>
          ))}
        </Grid>
      </Box>

      <Box className="cta-section">
        <Button variant="outlined" size="large" onClick={() => navigate('/contact')}>
          Get in Touch
        </Button>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Home;
